-30|title=5 reasons Gov. Cuomo and Dr. Fauci are America's de facto leaders during the coronavirus pandemic|last=Smith|first=Virginia K.|website=MarketWatch|access-date=March 30, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330201903/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/5-reasons-gov-cuomo-and-dr-fauci-are-americas-de-facto-leaders-during-the-coronavirus-pandemic-2020-03-30|archive-date=2020-03-30|url-status=no}}</ref>，并坚决主张在美国进行不断的[[保持社交距離|保持社交距離]]努力<ref name="Time Social">{{cite news|url=https://time.com/5812439/trump-coronavirus-measures-fauci/|title=President Trump's Advisors 'Argued Strongly' Against Easing Coronavirus Measures Too Early, Anthony Fauci Says|website=Time|access-date=March 30, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330150259/https://time.com/5812439/trump-coronavirus-measures-fauci/|archive-date=2020-03-30|url-status=no}}</ref>。

2020年新型冠狀病毒流傳期間，佛奇常態性參與[[白宮|白宮]]防疫記者會而為人所知，其在眾多意見上與白宮政治人物的看法多次截然不同也見諸報端，<ref>[https://www.guancha.cn/internation/2020_03_23_543320.shtml 福奇偷笑事件後受訪]</ref><ref>[https://www.worldjournal.com/6850539/article-%E5%A5%8E%E5%AF%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%89%B9%E6%95%88%E8%97%A5-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%88%87%E4%BD%9B%E5%A5%87%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83%E5%90%84%E8%AA%AA%E5%90%84%E8%A9%B1-%E6%B0%91/ 川普與佛奇記者會各說各話 民眾傻眼]</ref> 尤其4月份一種[[奎寧|奎寧]]能治療新冠的說法浮上檯面後佛奇與[[唐納·川普|川普]]總統以及貿易代表納瓦羅等非醫學專業的人士有巨大分歧，認為這是沒有嚴肅醫學研究的流言，只有一兩篇未經驗證的案例文章在流傳。之後有歐洲報導稱更多研究發現奎寧沒太大功效反而還增加死亡率，奎寧論點逐漸在白宮記者會上消失。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.worldjournal.com/6906763/article-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AE%8A%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9F-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%B7%E9%8A%B7%E5%A5%8E%E5%AF%A7-%E4%B8%8D%E7%8C%9C%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E8%B5%B0-%E4%BD%86%E7%85%A7%E7%BD%B5%E9%80%99/ |title=奎寧沒太大功效 |access-date=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200515194532/https://www.worldjournal.com/6906763/article-%e5%b7%9d%e6%99%ae%e8%ae%8a%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f-%e4%b8%8d%e5%bc%b7%e9%8a%b7%e5%a5%8e%e5%af%a7-%e4%b8%8d%e7%8c%9c%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e4%bd%95%e6%99%82%e8%b5%b0-%e4%bd%86%e7%85%a7%e7%bd%b5%e9%80%99/ |archive-date=2020-05-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/05/coronavirus-fauci-trump-anti-malaria-drug |title=Fauci: no evidence anti-malaria drug pushed by Trump works against virus |access-date=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200604002147/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/05/coronavirus-fauci-trump-anti-malaria-drug |archive-date=2020-06-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其極端重視科學現實沒有政治語言論點的態度意外在美國民眾間贏得好感，高於兩黨政治人物。<ref>[https://xw.qq.com/cmsid/20200330A0C6CA00 福克斯民调]</ref>

2020年5月份佛奇接受《[[國家地理_(雜誌)|国家地理]]》訪問時針對政治圈開始炒作的病毒起源論以及中國責任論等，他表示這是一種無意義的討論，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/469243/%E8%88%87%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E7%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D-%E7%A6%8F%E5%A5%87%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%BA%90%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97%E5%AE%A4%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95 |title=佛奇稱實驗室理論為無稽之談 |access-date=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531053759/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/469243/%E8%88%87%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E7%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D-%E7%A6%8F%E5%A5%87%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%BA%90%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97%E5%AE%A4%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>新冠病毒的結構經過科學界大量研究，其不可能是人類已知科技能人為創造出的。至於另一種陰謀論結構為「有人在野外發現病毒帶回[[實驗室|實驗室]]，然後從實驗室洩漏」這種論述類型的故事，本質是一種自我循环论证（circular argument，指逻辑上自己证实自己的谬论）的無意義討論，是一種永無結果的浪費時間，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nationalgeographic.com/science/2020/05/anthony-fauci-no-scientific-evidence-the-coronavirus-was-made-in-a-chinese-lab-cvd/ |title=nationalgeographic.com |access-date=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200606022112/https://www.nationalgeographic.com/science/2020/05/anthony-fauci-no-scientific-evidence-the-coronavirus-was-made-in-a-chinese-lab-cvd/ |archive-date=2020-06-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一個可傳染人的病毒若已成形且存在野外那可以有任何途徑散播，不論是否存在那假想中的實驗室或洩漏事件其本質對大流行都影響甚微且你永遠也無法有證據去論證。最後他鼓勵公眾從同行审议制的嚴謹科学期刊上找疫情訊息，少聽信媒體上評論員和政治圈的發言。<ref>[https://www.guancha.cn/internation/2020_05_05_549302.shtml 佛奇專訪間接駁斥總統和國務卿]</ref>

